summary: TL*THE CONTACT OWNS A 1989 EVELAND SCAMP CAMPER. THE CONTACT STATED THAT THE FRAME BROKE IN HALF WHILE THE VEHICLE WAS TRAVELING 35 MPH. THERE WERE NO SIGNS OF RUST ON THE FRAME. THE CONTACT HAD THE FRAME WELDED AND LEFT IT IN STORAGE. THE VIN WAS UNAVAILABLE. THE CURRENT AND FAILURE MILEAGES WERE UNKNOWN. UPDATED 06/01/11*LJ  UPDATED 01/04/2012 *LN
